The paper discusses end-to-end election verifiability, which involves ensuring the integrity and security of electronic voting systems. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including cryptography (cs.CR), cyber security (cs.CY), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and software engineering (cs.SE).
